author: jdcasey
msg: [MASSEMBLY-197] Use <useProjectArtifact>false</useProjectArtifact> in a dependencySet to keep it from processing the project artifact, and use <useProjectAttachments>true</useProjectAttachments> in a dependencySet to allow it to process the project's attached artifacts. The opposite of these flag values (true, false respectively) are the defaults.
